# Claude Code Configuration for Wedding Game Project

## Project Overview
Complete game framework with sophisticated systems ready for content creation.

### Development Approach
- User provides creative direction and design decisions
- Claude Code implements using existing systems
- Focus on content creation rather than system architecture

## ðŸ“‹ EXISTING SYSTEMS (DO NOT RECREATE)

### âœ… COMPLETE AUTOLOAD SYSTEMS:
- **GameManager.gd** (193 lines) - Game state, level progression, character unlocking
- **AudioManager.gd** (216 lines) - Music, SFX, character sounds, fade in/out
- **SpriteManager.gd** (311 lines) - Sprite management, placeholder generation
- **StateMachine.gd** (198 lines) - State machine for all entities
- **DialogueManager** - Full dialogue system addon
- **DynamicDialogueSystem** - Custom dialogue autoload

### âœ… COMPLETE CONFIGURATION:
- **project.godot** - All autoloads registered, input mapping, physics layers
- **Main.tscn** - Entry scene exists and configured
- **Main.gd** - Main game loop script

### âœ… COMPLETE FEATURES:
- **Character System** - 6 characters defined with animations
- **Level Progression** - Unlock system with dependencies
- **Save/Load** - JSON-based persistence
- **Audio System** - Bus management, character-specific sounds
